E. Westbrook <ewmgoe@westbrook.com>

Clean, proper, and up-to-date Gentoo ebuilds for MythTV.

Full documentation at:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/

Setup:

$ mkdir -pv /usr/local/overlays
$ cd /usr/local/overlays
$ git clone git://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo.git
$ echo 'PORTDIR_OVERLAY="$PORTDIR_OVERLAY /usr/local/overlays/ew-mythtv-gentoo"' >> /etc/make.conf
$ for i in media-plugins/myth{archive,browser,flix,gallery,movies,music,news,video,weather,zoneminder} x11-themes/mythtv-themes{,-extra} ; do echo "$i" >> /etc/portage/package.mask ; done
$ for i in media-tv/mythtv media-plugins/mythplugins x11-themes/myththemes www-apps/mythweb ; do echo $i >> /etc/portage/package.unmask ; done
$ emerge -Cav mythtv mythweb mythtv-themes mythtv-themes-extra mytharchive mythbrowser mythflix mythgallery mythgame mythmovies mythmusic mythnetvision mythnews mythvideo mythweather mythzoneminder
$ emerge -tav mythtv mythplugins mythweb myththemes

Updating:

$ cd /usr/local/overlays/ew-mythtv-gentoo
$ git pull
$ emerge -utavDN world

Auto-updating:

$ CRONSEC=$RANDOM ; let "CRONSEC %= 60" ; (crontab -l | grep -v '#' ; echo "$CRONSEC 1 * * * cd /usr/local/overlays/ew-mythtv-gentoo ; git pull") | crontab -

Full documentation at:
https://github.com/ewestbrook/ew-mythtv-gentoo/wiki/
